Name: TorqueConverterLockupEngaged
Comment: State signal which indicates whether the torque converter lockup is engaged. No torque converter on Volvo AMT...

Name: TransmissionShiftInProcess
Comment: Indicates that the transmission is in process of shifting from the current gear to the selected gear.

Name: TransmissionOutputShaftSpeed
Comment: Calculated speed of the transmission output shaft.

Name: ProgressiveShiftDisable
Comment: Command signal used to indicate that progressive shifting by the engine should be disallowed. not sent for AMTE

Name: TransInputShaftSpeed
Comment: Rotational velocity of the primary shaft transferring power into the transmission.

Name: SrcAddrssOfCtrllngDvcFrTrnsCtrl
Comment: The source address of the SAE J1939 device currently controlling the transmission. not sent by AMTE...
